{"word":"G5029 - τάχα - tácha - takh'-ah - Peradventure","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τάχα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">tácha</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">takh'-ah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Peradventure</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஒருவேளை, அநேகமாக - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"1. hastily, quickly, soon"},{"paragraph":"2. perhaps, peradventure"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>As if neuter plural of <a href=\"#/G5036 - ταχύς - tachýs - takh-oos'/5036\">G5036</a> (adverbially); <i>shortly</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>possibly:</i> - peradventure (-haps).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}